feeds.description:
ODM celebrated 30 years of God's goodness & faithfulness. It was a wonderful time of thanksgiving at Jerusalem Church, Gandhinagar. Nearly 450 people gathered. 
It was time of sharing testimonies, and hearing God's Word. Sarees were distributed to the widows as a token, a love and honor to them. Also food fellowship was arranged. 
All the Glory to our Lord Jesus!
